- sudo apt-get install nginx
- sudo systemctl stop/reload nginx 
- context || directives
- location blocks == перехват запроса, sample /greet || = /greet(full match)
- workers == quantity of the CPU cores (auto, lproc, lscpu)
- ulimit -n == amount of file descriptors
- dynamic models are available == ./configure --help | grep "dynamic"
- expires => to have cache on browser side
- gzip == compression of the content
- limits:
parallel connections
simultaneous connctions

